mods.abstract: Detained in the Jail of St. John the Baptist, a negro man calling himself WILLIAM, saying to be the property of Thomas Randall of New Orleans, said negro measuring 6 feet, speaks english only and wearing all his beard, is about 30 years old. NUMA TREPAGNIER. Dty Sheriff.
